---
title: Creepy Caribbean Chicken & Roasted Potato with Cursed Corn Slaw & Smokey Aioli
description: Did you hear that? Something just made a noise that sounds oddly like a rumbling stomach. It's best to offer this hungry beast a creamy and charred corn slaw with some crisp roast potatoes. If that isn't enough, we heard it's favourite is chicken with a startling Caribbean jerk seasoning. That should placate any hungry beast at your table.
